Sehr geehrter Benutzer, Sie müssen ein Identitätsdokument hochladen, um Ihr Konto zu bestätigen. Stellen Sie bei der Hochladung sicher, dass die Datei die folgenden Anforderungen entspricht:

•           Der Dateityp sollte JPG, PNG, GIF oder PDF sein und die Größe von 3 MB nicht überschreiten.  

•           Die Gültigkeit des Dokuments sollte nicht abgelaufen sein.

•           Das Foto sollte farbig sein (nicht schwarz und weiß).

•           Das Foto sollte aus dem Originaldokument stammen. Digitale Fotomontage ist nicht erlaubt.

•           Das Foto, die persönlichen Daten, die Unterschrift, das Siegel und andere Daten des Dokuments sollten deutlich sichtbar sein.

•           Falls erforderlich, kann das Unternehmen andere Dokumente anfordern.

ger.close-account-text:
You can close your account at vbet.com at any time. By confirming this action you will be immediately disconnected from the website and will not be able to use this account any more. However, you will be able to open a new account.

If at the moment of the closure your account balance is positive and you have verified your account, the balance amount will be transfered to your account within 48 hours.

If at the moment of the closure your account balance is positive but you have not verified your account, the balance amount will be transferred to your bank account only after sending your verification documents for validation. Please note that your balance amount can be kept for 6 years starting from the account closure date. Upon expiration of this period, the amount will be transferred to the State.

ger.freebet_info:
Vbet betting company offers its customers a free quiz.
Customers will be offered 3 types of express, which contains 6, 8 or 10 events. If the customer guesses correctly 6 out of 6 events and the winning amount will be 15$ , 8 out of 8 events the payout will be 30$ , and if you guess 10 out of 10 events the payoff will be 40$. The winning amount will be transferred to the customer’s account within 5 days after completion of all events are included in all 3 express bets.
If there are events, which have not taken place in this variant of express, the quiz will be lost.
Each customer can daily make an express bet on each variant only once.
